__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: Culture Of Honor
title: Culture Of Honor
description: What does honor look like? How can you foster and build an atmosphere of honor around you? Don’t miss out on this incredible episode of Miracles Happen with our special guest, Pastor Dan Daniels. He shares about a core value that he holds of importance in his own life–– that being honor. We are called to love God and one another in the greatest commandments within the Bible. But where do we start? How are love and honor connected in this? Find out by joining us for the wisdom God has poured out and revealed to Pastor Dan in the area of honor, as he imparts these revelations to you. Pastor Dan will help you discover what honor is, how to recognize and show honor to others, and steps to building a culture of honor in your own life. Let’s start today in taking steps to living out honor in every area of our lives!
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: The Commitment Of An Overcomer
title: The Commitment Of An Overcomer
description: Have you ever ordered a steak that was well done on the outside, but raw on the inside? That’s how some churches look today…well-cooked on the outside, but half-baked on the inside. __str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Preparation For Glory
title: Preparation For Glory
description: Tony Evans explores the concept of entering heaven victoriously and abundantly. Drawing from the book of 2 Peter, he emphasizes the importance of knowing and experiencing God in order to receive His multiplied grace and peace. Evans highlights that every believer already possesses everything they need for a victorious Christian life, as it is granted by God's divine power. He challenges listeners to diligently apply themselves to the growth of their new divine nature, escaping the corruption of the world and becoming partakers of God's nature.

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: Image of God
title: Image of God
description: Do you want to learn how to engage the world without compromising your faith? Don't miss Miracles Happen with guest Tomi Arayomi that will transform your perspective on your true identity and purpose. In this captivating episode, Tomi Arayomi takes us on an enlightening journey, explaining the divine nature of Jesus and His role as the image of God in our lives. He delves deep into scripture with the message that unveils the profound concept of the Image of God within you. Discover how you are intricately connected to this divine image and are uniquely made in the image of the Lord God. Get ready to explore the profound connection between God's rest, Jesus' mission, and your role in subduing the enemy's schemes. Tomi Arayomi will teach you why you are God's best answer to confront the challenges of this world. It's time to unlock the supernatural potential within you and embrace your true image of God. Don't miss this life-changing episode of Miracles Happen! Watch and be inspired to walk in your divine identity and purpose TODAY!
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: The Issachar Anointing
title: The Issachar Anointing
description:
Join me for this captivating episode of "Miracles Happen" as we welcome guest Bishop Robert Stearns. He dives into the profound wisdom of the Issachar anointing, sharing about spiritual discernment and divine transitions. 

Learn how the sons of Issachar understood the times and gained insight into navigating transitions in life and faith. Bishop Stearns unpacks the biblical story of Saul and David, revealing crucial lessons about repentance, obedience, and the condition of the heart. Tune in and gain valuable insights on how to align with God's purposes amidst delays and challenges, drawing inspiration from biblical figures like David and Nehemiah.
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: Miracles Happen!  with Joan Hunter
title: Miracles Happen!  with Joan Hunter
description: Join me in this heartfelt episode of "Miracles Happen" as I delve into the profound significance of Jesus's life, death, and resurrection. Together, we will explore the personal depth of Jesus's sacrifice and its transformative power in our lives today. From bearing stripes for healing to dying of a broken heart, I will unpack the profound love behind Jesus's actions and their tangible impact on our daily existence. Discover the power of communion, the authority bestowed upon us as believers, and the promise of healing and blessings. Experience Easter in a new light as I invite you to reflect on Jesus's sacrifice and embrace the abundant life He offers. Don't miss this uplifting journey of faith and divine revelation!
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: A Mother's Love
title: A Mother's Love
description: Join me in this special Mother's Day edition of "Miracles Happen" as I shares heartfelt stories, practical advice, and words of encouragement for all the amazing and wonderful mothers everywhere. Discover the power and authority that mothers and mother-figures hold in shaping each and every one of the lives of their children, and learn how to navigate the journey of motherhood with wisdom and grace. Don't miss this empowering episode filled with inspiration and hope for mothers of all ages. Let's honor and show love and appreciation this week and year around for the self-less women, who have played vital roles in our lives through motherhood, in helping us grow into who we are today!

title: The Mystery Of Godliness
description: The mystery of godliness is connected to the uniqueness and Person of Jesus Christ.  Godliness is God depositing in us His mediator of grace, Jesus Christ. Therefore, Jesus Christ is our only key to a life of godliness.

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: God's Prophetic Calendar
title: God's Prophetic Calendar
description: Since we're still here, we still have some time to make things right.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Keep Digging Your Ditches
title: Keep Digging Your Ditches
description: Join Dr. Tony Evans as he guides us into greater spiritual wholeness through his teachings—and begin to enjoy God’s Word, and His presence, like never before. Be sure to subscribe so you never miss an upload.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: The Power Of Fatherhood
title: The Power Of Fatherhood
description: Tune in with me for this heartfelt Father's Day episode of "Miracles Happen" as we celebrate the significance of fathers in helping shaping their families. Drawing from my own personal journey and experiences, I will emphasize the power of a father's words in influencing the lives of their children. From overcoming challenges to finding one's identity, I offer wisdom and encouragement for fathers to embrace their role with love, intentionality, and empowerment. Discover the transformative impact of fatherhood and learn how to speak life into your children, leaving a lasting legacy of love and faith. Don't miss this inspiring message of hope and healing for fathers everywhere. Happy Father's Day!
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Faith For Your Journey
title: Faith For Your Journey
description: Dr. Tony Evans looks at 2 Peter 1:1-11, emphasizing the importance of living a useful and fruitful life through faith. He explains Peter's twofold goal for believers: to live productively and to enter heaven victoriously. Dr. Evans stresses that every Christian has the divine nature implanted within them, but this must be cultivated through diligent faith and action.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: Stand Firm
title: Stand Firm
description:
Are you ready to experience a powerful episode as we welcome guests Sean and Christa Smith, an inspiring duo with a heart for revival? 

Tune in for Miracles Happen, as Christa shares profound wisdom on the importance of your positioning in this critical hour, calling you as a believers to stand firm in your purpose despite the warfare you may face. Journey with Sean as he takes you through captivating stories of supernatural healing encounters, showcasing the accessibility of God's miraculous power that you can have in your life.
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Seeking God's Kingdom First
title: Seeking God's Kingdom First
description: God does not want to be one of many things in your life. He wants to be FIRST. And seeking Him first means you are going to FIRST take care of God's business so that He can take care of your business.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: with Tomi Arayomi
title: with Tomi Arayomi
description: Do you want to learn how to engage the world without compromising your faith? Don't miss Miracles Happen with guest Tomi Arayomi that will transform your perspective on your true identity and purpose. In this captivating episode, Tomi Arayomi takes us on an enlightening journey, explaining the divine nature of Jesus and His role as the image of God in our lives. He delves deep into scripture with the message that unveils the profound concept of the Image of God within you. Discover how you are intricately connected to this divine image and are uniquely made in the image of the Lord God. Get ready to explore the profound connection between God's rest, Jesus' mission, and your role in subduing the enemy's schemes. Tomi Arayomi will teach you why you are God's best answer to confront the challenges of this world. It's time to unlock the supernatural potential within you and embrace your true image of God. Don't miss this life-changing episode of Miracles Happen! Watch and be inspired to walk in your divine identity and purpose TODAY!
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: Miracles Happen! :: 2 :: God's Master Plan
title: God's Master Plan
description: Do you want to see the supernatural power of God show up & show out in your life? Tune in for an amazing new episode of Miracles Happen with special guest Bobby Conner as he teaches you to get up, get off the sideline, get in the frontline, and enjoy Jesus!
season: Miracles Happen! :: 2

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Giving To God First
title: Giving To God First
description: Some of us go to church in stolen clothes. Some drive to church in stolen cars and live in stolen homes. How many bites out of the apple will you take before giving to God?
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Seeing Gods Provision
title: Seeing Gods Provision
description: Cultural trends and events can cause a disruption in our lives that we may not be entirely comfortable with. In this message, we’ll explore a classic message from Dr. Evans as he takes a look at the life of the prophet Elijah, revealing that there’s plenty we can learn in times of disorder.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Living Faith
title: Living Faith
description: Join Dr. Tony Evans as he guides us into greater spiritual wholeness through his teachings—and begin to enjoy God’s Word, and His presence, like never before. Be sure to subscribe so you never miss an upload.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Living A Life That Lasts
title: Living A Life That Lasts
description: When life gets thorny, many times our only instinct is to do whatever it takes to get things back to normal. But in this message, Dr. Evans took listeners to the book of Exodus to show that God often has something better in mind for us through those uncomfortable times.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Committing To The True God
title: Committing To The True God
description: Many people who say they trust in God also put their trust in a lot of other things. In this message, we’ll take a look at why anything short of total commitment to Christ simply falls short.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: The Prayer For Spiritual Power
title: The Prayer For Spiritual Power
description: Dr. Tony Evans shares the keys to Igniting Kingdom Prayer in our lives.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Claiming Your Legal Rights
title: Claiming Your Legal Rights
description: As Christians, we're saved by grace, not the law. But Dr. Evans explains that God's law guarantees you certain rights you can depend on when you're facing problems or pain. Discover why God is waiting for his people to stand up and claim those rights, and why so few actually do.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Understanding Spiritual Authority
title: Understanding Spiritual Authority
description: Dr. Tony Evans shares the keys to Igniting Kingdom Prayer in our lives.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Praying In Jesus' Name
title: Praying In Jesus' Name
description: Dr. Tony Evans shares the keys to Igniting Kingdom Prayer in our lives.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Piggybacking On Jesus' Authority
title: Piggybacking On Jesus' Authority
description: Join Dr. Tony Evans as he guides us into greater spiritual wholeness through his teachings—and begin to enjoy God’s Word, and His presence, like never before. Be sure to subscribe so you never miss an upload.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: The Kingdom Power of Prayer
title: The Kingdom Power of Prayer
description: God has unlimited power; we have continuing needs. It literally seems like a match made in heaven. So why aren't more believers seeing their needs met? Find out as Dr. Tony Evans explains why we must surrender our control before God will let us use some of his.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: The Authority Of Binding And Loosing
title: The Authority Of Binding And Loosing
description: If you grew up in church, you’re probably familiar with the concept of binding and loosing. But Dr. Tony Evans wants to take you deeper into its meaning than you’ve ever been before by helping you understand how to apply these two ideas to your own life. Learn how binding and loosing is meant to function in order to help you exercise your kingdom authority.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Praying To Change God's Mind
title: Praying To Change God's Mind
description: Have you ever wondered if it’s possible for God—an omniscient, never-changing being who exists outside of time—to simply change His mind? Well, Dr. Tony Evans says the answer might not be what you would expect. In this message on the life of Hezekiah, learn how it’s possible for God to reverse His decisions when prayer is brought into the equation.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Praying To Move Mountains
title: Praying To Move Mountains
description: We’ve all faced mountains throughout our lives—situations that loom so large you can’t find a way over or through it. Well, Jesus tells us we have the power to move these mountains, but many Christians wind up placing a lot of faith in the wrong things. In this message, Tony Evans discusses how prayer and just the smallest amount of faith in the right thing can set you free from the mountains that hold you hostage. .
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: God, Justice, And Righteousness
title: God, Justice, And Righteousness
description: Dr. Tony Evans emphasizes the critical importance of righteousness and justice as the two staples of God’s governance in society. He explains that a nation’s stability and moral foundation depend on adherence to divine laws rather than human opinions. True societal reform must start with spiritual atonement, which leads to justice and mercy in action, ultimately demonstrating the need for the Church to embody these principles.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: God And Family
title: God And Family
description: God is the designer of the family, but our culture has been eroding the foundations of the family for decades. When the family crumbles, society is soon to follow, and we’re seeing the indications of that today. Discover how God has designed the government and the family to fit together to fulfill His purposes for a better society.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: God,  Church, And State
title: God,  Church, And State
description: The Constitution guarantees us freedom of religion, but Dr. Tony Evans says that too many people have taken that to mean freedom from religion. In this message, he’ll talk about why God created governments in the first place and explain why the influence and involvement of faithful people is a vital part of keeping them on track.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: God And Civil Leaders
title: God And Civil Leaders
description: Dr. Tony Evans says being a “kingdom voter” means godly values guide our decisions about policies and people. In this message, he’ll talk about the connection between God and civil leaders and offer biblical advice about how to recognize candidates with character.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: God And Conscience
title: God And Conscience
description: Dr. Tony Evans challenges Christians to prioritize God’s kingdom over earthly political divisions, advocating for “kingdom voting” where voters align their choices with biblical principles.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: God And Citizenship
title: God And Citizenship
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: The Living Water
title: The Living Water
description: Living Water flows and transforms the environment it is in. Like that water, the Holy Spirit transforms our souls when He flows through us. In this message, Dr. Evans explains how to transform your soul through The Living Water.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: Loving God First
title: Loving God First
description: Have you forgotten your first love? Many of us want God's blessings, but we don't want Him nor do we want Him first. In his current sermon series, Dr. Evans challenges us to return God to His rightful place: First.
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6 :: The Lord
title: The Lord
season: The Urban Alternative with Dr. Tony Evans :: 6

__str__: Grey Matter :: 1 :: Why Faith Is as Important as Health
title: Why Faith Is as Important as Health
description: What are you called to do? Author Shilo Creed knows her calling—to write novels, and she’s written 38 of them. She shares how a major health scare challenged her beliefs and led her to a deeper, more functional faith—one that truly works when tested. She explains why developing our spiritual side is just as essential as physical health, because when life’s challenges come, only a strong, trained faith can move mountains.
season: Grey Matter :: 1
